 experiencing a resurgence of interest among students and educators of calculus today.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aCalculus. 0aProcesses, Infinite. 7aMATHEMATICS / General.2bisacsh1 aBressoud, David.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311063538640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226806693423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226806693.jpg  a978-3-11-063538-6  University of Chicago Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles